de.mrapp.android.tabswitcher.layout.tablet

Class TabletTabRecyclerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mrapp.android.util.view.AbstractViewRecycler.Adapter<AbstractItem,java.lang.Integer>
      • de.mrapp.android.tabswitcher.layout.AbstractTabRecyclerAdapter
        • de.mrapp.android.tabswitcher.layout.tablet.TabletTabRecyclerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Model.Listener, Tab.Callback

    public class TabletTabRecyclerAdapter
extends AbstractTabRecyclerAdapter
    A view recycler adapter, which allows to inflate the views, which are used to visualize the tabs of a TabSwitcher, when using the tablet layout.
    Since:
    1.0.0
